  04 Feb 2008; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> xcolor-2.11.ebuild:
  Stable for HPPA (bug #208747).

  03 Feb 2008; Christian Faulhammer <opfer@gentoo.org> xcolor-2.11.ebuild:
  stable x86, bug 208747

  03 Feb 2008; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org> xcolor-2.11.ebuild:
  generate fonts in the sandbox instead of using addwrite..

  18 Dec 2007; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> xcolor-2.11.ebuild:
  Marked ~hppa (bug #195815).

  27 Oct 2007; Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org> xcolor-2.00-r1.ebuild,
  xcolor-2.11.ebuild:
  Dropped ppc-macos keyword, see you in prefix

  26 Oct 2007; Raúl Porcel <armin76@gentoo.org> xcolor-2.11.ebuild:
  Add ~ia64

  25 Oct 2007; Markus Rothe <corsair@gentoo.org> xcolor-2.11.ebuild:
  Added ~ppc64

*xcolor-2.11 (14 Oct 2007)

  14 Oct 2007; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org> +xcolor-2.11.ebuild:
  version bump, make use of texmf-site, depend on tex packages that support it

  12 Mar 2007; Alexandre Buisse <nattfodd@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Replaced text-markup by tex as maintaining herd (text-markup split).

  22 Feb 2007; Piotr Jaroszyński <peper@gentoo.org> ChangeLog:
  Transition to Manifest2.

